strong>SDC357 &ndash; The importance of U.S. food and agricultural trade in a new global market environment</strong><br />\n<strong>WDC34 &ndash; Institute for Range Sheep Production</strong></p>\n<p>************************************************************</p>\n<p>To View the Proposal:</p>\n<p>1. Go to the National Information Management Support System at <a href="http://nimss.umd.edu">http://nimss.umd.edu</a></p>\n<p>2. Insert your login and password. (If you don&#8217;t have a login ID, you&#8217;ll need to register, also at the URL above.  If you forgot, please use the &#8220;Track ID&#8221; function on the login page.  Please do not re-register.)</p>\n<p>3. In theTop Menu, Select Project then Select View Projects</p>\n<p>4. Enter the project number</p>\n<p>************************************************************</p>\n<p>To Create and Submit an Appendix E for a Proposed Project:</p>\n<p>1. Go to the National Information Management Support System at <a href="http://nimss.umd.edu">http://nimss.umd.edu</a></p>\n<p>2. Insert your login and password. (If you don&#8217;t have a login, you&#8217;ll need to register, also at the above URL.)</p>\n<p>3. In theTop Menu, Select Participants then Select Draft/Edit</p>\n<p>4. On the Left side Menu, Select &#8220;Draft New&#8221;</p>\n<p>5. Select the project number</p>\n<p>6. Fill out the form.</p>\n<p>7. Click on Submit.</p>\n<p><strong>Please Contact Casey Hillmer at 608-262-2397 or <a href="mailto:aseitler@cals.wisc.edu">clhillmer@cals.wisc.edu</a> before you create an Appendix E to add your participation to a proposed multistate project.</strong></p>\n<p>Thank you. Please contact the Administrative Advisor of the multistate project if you have questions about the proposed project.</p>\n<p>**************************************************************</p>\n<p>Contact Chris Hamilton at 608-262-2349 or <a href="mailto:chamilton@cals.wisc.edu">chamilton@cals.wisc.edu</a> if you have questions about the use of NIMSS.</p>\n<p>Contact Casey Hillmer at 608-262-2397 or <a href="mailto:aseitler@cals.wisc.edu">clhillmer@cals.wisc.edu</a> if you have questions about your participation.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:99:"http://ecals.cals.wisc.edu/research/2013/07/23/multistate-proposals-inviting-participation-19/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:69:"\n		\n		\n		\n 		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:15:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"CALS Ice Cream Social this Friday, Ag Hall, 1–3 p.m.";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:99:"http://ecals.cals.wisc.edu/highlights/2013/07/22/cals-ice-cream-social-this-friday-ag-hall-1-3-p-m/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:13:"featuredimage";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"meetingDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"attachments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:22:"additionalResourcesUrl";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b