ity to help Milwaukee-area children in need by collecting school supply donations at a State Fair admissions entrance. In addition to volunteering for a great cause, you will receive free admission to the State Fair, plus a complimentary t-shirt. Learn more and sign up today at <a href="http://www.statefair.wisc.edu/volunteer.html">statefair.wisc.edu/volunteer</a></p>\n<p>While enjoying the State Fair, celebrate the spirit and tradition of UW-Madison. There is something for everyone: hands-on scientific demonstrations, live presentations, performances, games, and, of course, the pep rally and parade.</p>\n<p>We hope you are available to volunteer with us on Wednesday, August 7! If you have any questions, please email <a href="mailto:volunteer@uwmad.wisc.edu">volunteer@uwmad.wisc.edu</a>.</p>\n<p><i> </i></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:108:"http://ecals.cals.wisc.edu/extension-outreach/2013/06/25/volunteer-at-uw-madison-day-at-the-state-fair/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:52;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:72:"\n		\n		\n		\n 		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:15:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"Needed: Stories that show the impact of gifts to CALS";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:106:"http://ecals.cals.wisc.edu/extension-outreach/2013/06/24/needed-stories-about-the-impact-of-gift