"http://grow.cals.wisc.edu/departments/on-henry-mall/class-act-hardwood-and-soft-skills">Grow magazine Class Act</a> article, Wells&#8217; duties with the FFA include going out to middle and high schools, where he encourages FFA members to get active in the program and talks with them about the importance of “soft” skills—a positive attitude, good work habits, teamwork and other traits that can put them on the path to success.</p>\n<p>“I get to tell them my story and inspire them to do something like that for themselves,” Wells says.</p>\n<p>The <a href="http://www.wisconsinffa.org/index.php">Wisconsin FFA</a> is a youth organization dedicated to making a positive difference in the lives of young people by developing their potential for leadership, personal growth and career success through agricultural education.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:105:"http://ecals.cals.wisc.edu/teaching-advising/2013/06/17/logan-wells-becomes-wisconsin-ffa-president/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:62;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:69:"\n		\n		\n		\n 		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:15:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:42:"CALS in the News for the Week of June 8-14";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:131:"http://ecals.cals.wisc.edu/extension-outreach/cals-in-the-news-awards-honors/2013/06/14/cals-in-the-news