p>\n<ul>\n<li>Introductions</li>\n<li>Review agenda</li>\n<li>Review charge and function and APC’s role</li>\n<li>Review minutes, May 14, 2013 and June 19, 2013</li>\n<li>Revisions to current agenda</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">Action and Discussion Items</span></p>\n<p>1.   Strategic Planning update</p>\n<p>2. Five-year review of APC structure and function</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Definition of a “quorum” and inclusion of academic staff</li>\n<li>Reconsider APC districts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.   Biology update</p>\n<p>4. Upcoming academic program issues</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Development Economics Option in AAE undergraduate major</li>\n<li>CALS Business Certificate</li>\n<li>Plant Sciences Option in undergraduate Biology major, being proposed by Horticulture, Agronomy, et. al.</li>\n<li>Zoology graduate program name change</li>\n<li>Neuroscience Major</li>\n<li>Undergraduate Sustainability Certificate</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>CASI members and Divisions</strong>:</p>\n<p>Animal Sciences:  Tom Crenshaw<br />\nBasic Sciences:  Karen Wassarman<br />\nExtension: Carrie  Laboski<br />\nFood and Nutrition:  David Eide<br />\nPhysical Sciences:  Sundaram Gunasekaran<br />\nPlant Sciences:  Ann MacGuidwin<br />\nNatural Sciences:  Ken Raffa<br />\nSocial Sciences:  Leann Tigges<br />\nAcademic Staff, elected: Robin  Kurtz<br />\nAcademic Staff, CASI rep: TBA</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b>Meeting Dates:   </b></p>\n<p>September 3 – 3:00-4:30 p.m., 354 Agricultural Hall<br />\nSeptember 17 – 3:00-4:30 p.m., 354 Agricultural Hall<br />\nOctober 1 – 1:00-3:30 p.m., 6201 Microbial Sciences Building (Joint with L&amp;S)<br />\nOctober 15 – 1:00-3:30 p.m., 6201 Microbial Sciences Building (Joint with L&amp;S)<br />\nNovember 5 – 3:00-4:30 p.m., 354 Agricultural Hall<br />\nNovember 19 – 3:00-4:30 p.m., 354 Agricultural Hall<br />\nDecember 3 – 3:00-4:30 p.m., 354 Agricultural Hall<br />\nDecember 17 – 3:00-4:30 p.m., 354 Agricultural Hall</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s