and multistate) McIntire-Stennis (M-S) Projects (individual investigator and multidisciplinary) Animal Health Projects (individual investigator and multidisciplinary) Funding Period: FY 2015 [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"clhillmer";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2530:"<p>The Wisconsin Agricultural Experiment Station has issued its fiscal year 2015 call for proposals. A summary is provided below; to view the full call for proposals, visit <a href="http://www.cals.wisc.edu/waes/application/proposals.html" target="_blank">http://www.cals.wisc.edu/waes/application/proposals.html</a></p>\n<p><strong>Available Opportunities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><b>Hatch Projects</b> (individual investigator, multidisciplinary, and multistate)</li>\n<li><b>McIntire-Stennis</b> (M-S) Projects (individual investigator and multidisciplinary)</li>\n<li><b>Animal Health Projects</b> (individual investigator and multidisciplinary)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Funding Period:</strong> FY 2015 (October 1, 2014- September 30, 2015)</p>\n<p><strong>*Note: Deadline to request 5-year proposals due: <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Tuesday, August 6, 2013</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Submission Deadline: <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Friday, September 6, 2013, by 4:30 p.m.</span></strong></p>\n<p><em>Submit proposals to the CALS Research Division Office via WISPER.<br />\nRequests for deadline extensions will not be granted.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Submission Guidelines:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Proposals received after 4:30pm on September 6, 2013 will not be considered.</li>\n<li>Proposals must be submitted via the WISPER system.</li>\n<li>Proposals must include all approvals (Chair/Administrator/Co-PIs) in order to be considered.</li>\n<li>Attachments to the WISPER record must include budget worksheet, as well as a full proposal.<span style="font-style: italic; font-size: 14px;"><b>NOTE:</b> The budget worksheet now includes a timeline component. This additional tab in the budget worksheet document must be completed in order for proposals to be considered.</span></li>\n<li>Document type selected must be “Hatch”</li>\n<li>Proposals must be routed to Casey Hillmer</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Review Schedule:</strong> October 2013 – November 2013</p>\n<p><strong>Funding Decisions Announced:</strong> December 2013 – January 2014</p>\n<p><strong>Full Call for Proposals:</strong><br />\n<a href="http://www.cals.wisc.edu/waes/application/proposals.html">http://www.cals.wisc.edu/waes/application/proposals.html</a></p>\n<p><strong>For Additional Information/Assistance:</strong></p>\n<p>Angie Seitler at (608) 261-1432, <a href="mailto:aseitler@cals.wisc.edu">aseitler@cals.wisc.edu</a></p>\n<p>Casey Hillmer at (608) 262-2397, <a href="mailto:clhillmer@cals.wisc.edu">clhillmer@cals.wisc.edu</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:125:"http://ecals.cals.wisc.edu/research/2013/08/23/fy-15-hatch-mcintire-stennis-and-animal-health-call-for-proposals-due-96/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:11;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:72:"\n		\n		\n		\n 		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"